{"tid":839162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【恐怖分屍】老公恨妻「私生活」太精彩 殺人割頭掟落水井","createTime":"2018-09-27T17:08:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T00:55:18.000Z","uid":212249,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7e34d7f3f1eb142d668bdce3819c60bdbca43bfa","tid":839162,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T17:08:49.000Z","msg":"內地傳媒近日報道一宗安徽阜陽市駭人命案。上周六（22日）上午，太和縣皮條孫鎮一村落的芝麻地驚見一顆斷頭。死者為一名周姓已婚婦人，而兇手竟是其王姓丈夫。<br />\n<br />\n22日清晨6時許，皮條孫鎮葦張村委會范廟村一名范姓村民準備落田收割芝麻，期間發現地上有一個垃圾袋，細看下，驚見袋中竟是一顆腐爛的頭顱。警方調查後，發現死者為成年女性，已死亡3個月左右，死亡原因為機械性窒息死亡，兇手殺人肢解後棄屍。<br />\n<br />\n周二（25日）下午，警方鎖定死者為太和縣51歲周姓女村民，疑兇為55歲王姓丈夫。當晚警方曾到疑兇家人，惟未有發現，隨後得悉王男白天拉三輪車載客，每天晚飯後回家。警方在外守候，終於在晚上10時許抓獲王男。<br />\n<br />\n王男供述，妻子「私生活」多姿多彩，一直是夫妻間揮之不去的「刺」。今年7月10日，周婦不顧勸阻企圖再次外出。王男失去理智掐死妻子。為了逃避追捕，他肢解妻子，把頭顱扔進妻子娘家村莊不遠的一口機井內。村民取水時打撈膠袋上來，因臭氣熏天被以為是「死貓死狗」，隨手扔到旁邊芝麻地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/all/realtime/article/20180928/58731290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fall%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180928%2F58731290&d=%2BoX3ALZ8q%2FvQFAm0m5BtCDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=30e8befa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fall%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180928%2F58731290&h=b44c507c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/all/realtime/article/20180928/58731290</a>"},{"pid":"8158785505aaeba0db6e9dc5f4890dfdab6727ce","tid":839162,"uid":164913,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T17:13:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46258c67091473c0f09d54031325070fce6cbc00","tid":839162,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T19:42:45.000Z","msg":"「啲骨頭呢，重噉立亂抌喺村口度啊，真系冇陰功喇。」"},{"pid":"d9095fcad7d7f45a64a210f738ac26de07d33a08","tid":839162,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T23:53:39.000Z","msg":"綠<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38bf514bbe8ecacb8a29003d4308acca827ea04a","tid":839162,"uid":146376,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T00:02:22.000Z","msg":"做得冇錯 呢d賤女人就係要咁樣教訓下佢"},{"pid":"a48ac755948cdd37b5b8745087c297fc36e80803","tid":839162,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T00:03:21.000Z","msg":"有時幾佩服上面D人個種不顧一切後果"},{"pid":"4d493b436c5eccbd7aef1bcf053b722850f3bf91","tid":839162,"uid":55597,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T00:05:54.000Z","msg":"掉落水井，成條村玩完"},{"pid":"3449dd7f34e06fe3d0dffc713e7ae21b7555ee90","tid":839162,"uid":2470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T00:20:46.000Z","msg":"飲屍水<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6753d3664960e92f9612b0ee952c0dc7e4035d09","tid":839162,"uid":166288,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T00:23:09.000Z","msg":"生化攻擊食水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7585f2f3c797c8a8eb0b9c4219bc6cace42d4f63","tid":839162,"uid":10637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T00:25:40.000Z","msg":"如果發生係美國<br />\ncctvb一定會報"},{"pid":"2de872f552947e15f5546d697ad47664d424e7a0","tid":839162,"uid":211656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T00:55:18.000Z","msg":"大陸的 不意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}